TemplateFormate.template1Instructions: Mobile numbers should be specified in the subject line with coma separator and SMS message should be specified in the mail body.

TemplateFormate.template4Instructions: To address should contains mailbox, Mobile numbers should be in attached file (txt or csv) with SMS message in body to send bulk SMS
TemplateFormate.template5Instructions: To address contains mailbox, subject line should contain mobile numbers, and body should contain SMS message with [EndofMessaage] tag
TemplateFormate.template5AInstructions: To address contains mobile numbers as shown, subject line can be any, and body should contain SMS message with [EndofMessaage] tag
